{title}

{avgRating}{" "} Somewhere
{city} {price} / per person {distance} k/m {maxGroupSize} people
Decription

{desc}

{/* Tour review section */}

Reviews ({reviews?.length} reviews)

1 2 3 4 5
{ reviews?.map(review=>(
Alex

{new Date().toDateString()}

5
Amazing Tour
)) }
); }; export default TourDetails;
